'''梭状回'''（Fusiform gyrus）是[[颞叶|颞叶]]与[[枕叶|枕叶]]一部分，也被称作'''枕颞外侧回'''（lateral occipitotemporal gyrus），与枕颞内侧回（[[舌回|舌回]]、[[海马旁回|海马旁回]]）相对应。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Fusiform gyrus|url=http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/CentralDirectory.aspx?ID=139|access-date=2021-05-31|work=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603050017/http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/CentralDirectory.aspx?ID=139|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Fusiform gyrus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/fusiform-gyrus?lang=us|access-date=2021-05-31|last=Loh|first=Daniel|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104200813/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/fusiform-gyrus?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Nature Neuroscience, vol7, 2004</ref> 结构上，梭状回在[[布罗德曼分区系统|布罗德曼分区系统]]为37区，其外侧与内侧被浅的“梭状回中间[[脑沟|沟]]（mid-fusiform sulcus）”分开。<ref> Weiner et al. The mid-fusiform sulcus: A landmark identifying both cyotarchitectonic and functional divisions of human ventral temporal cortex. NeuroImage. 2013. http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.neuroimage.2013.08.068 </ref><ref>Weiner & Grill-Spector, Sparsely-distributed organization of face and limb activations in human ventral temporal cortex. NeuroImage. 2010 Oct 1;52(4):1559-73. Epub 2010 May 10.</ref><ref>Nasr el al. Scene-selective cortical regions in human and nonhuman primates. J Neurosci. 2011 Sep 28;31(39):13771-85.</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Gyrus|url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/fusiform+gyrus|accessdate=2013-06-19|publisher=The free dictionary|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130620043931/http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/fusiform+gyrus|archive-date=2013-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 结构 ==
梭状回与下方的[[颞下回|颞下回]]之间有[[枕颞沟|枕颞沟]]（occipitotemporal sulcus）相隔开，与上方的[[海马旁回|海马旁回]]、[[舌回|舌回]]之间有[[侧副裂|侧副裂]]隔开<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":222">{{Cite web|title=Medial occipitotemporal gyrus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/medial-occipitotemporal-gyrus?lang=us|access-date=2021-05-31|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105043548/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/medial-occipitotemporal-gyrus?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==功能==
科学界对梭状回功能有下述比较一致的认识：
# 处理颜色信息
# 人脸与身体识别 (见{{tsl|en|Fusiform face area|梭状回面孔区}})
# 文字识别 (见{{tsl|en|Visual word form area|视觉词形区}})
# 分类辨识

研究表明，梭状回与[[脸盲症|脸盲症]]，即面部辨识能力缺乏症，直接相关。<ref>McCarthy, G et al. Face-specific processing in the fuman fusform gyrus.''J. Cognitive Neuroscicence. 9, 605-610(1997).</ref>梭状回中负责人脸认知的部分称为{{tsl|en|Fusiform face area|梭状回面孔区}}（fusiform face area, FFA）。梭状回面孔区可以对不是脸的视觉形象产生像脸的认知，著名的例子如火星上的[[利比亚山|利比亚山]]与[[塞东尼亚区|塞东尼亚区]]。如果梭状回面孔区被破坏，就会失去辨识人脸的能力，就连最亲密的家人也无法认出来。眼睛负责感知视觉信息，经过视皮层处理后，再由梭状回辨析，找出生物特征，借此来分辨不同的人。梭状回面孔区中的'''内梭状回'''在接收到人臉信息时被激活，而且在害羞的人与善于社交的人的内梭状回表现不同。一项研究证实查看陌生人的图像时，害羞的成年人内梭状回活化的程度比善于社交的成年人显著地少。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Beaton, E. A., Schmidt, L. A., Schulkin, J., Antony, M. M., Swinson, R. P. & Hall, G. B.|year=2009|title=Different fusiform activity to stranger and personally familiar faces in shy and social adults|journal=Social Neuroscience|volume= 4|issue=4|pages=308–316|doi=10.1080/17470910902801021|pmid=19322727}}</ref>除此之外，另一项研究指出观看到吸引人的脸孔时内梭状回活化的程度会更高，主因为美丽的容貌唤起广泛的神经网络，包括知觉、奖励、决策等回路。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Chatterjee, A., Thomas, A., Smith, S. E., & Aguirre, G. K. |year=2009|title= The neural response to facial attractiveness|journal= Neuropsychology|volume= 23|issue=2|pages=135–143|doi=10.1037/a0014430|pmid=19254086}}</ref>

梭状体异常与[[威廉氏症候群|威廉氏症候群]]相关。<ref>A. L. Reiss, et al. Preliminary Evidence Of Abnormal White Matter Related To The Fusiform Gyrus In Williams Syndrome: A Diffusion Tensor Imaging Tractography Study.''Genes, Brain & Behavior 11.1, 62-68(2012)</ref> 梭状体也与表情的认知有关。<ref name=radua2010>
