梭状回面孔区增加活动程度可产生人脸幻觉，可能是真实人脸或者卡通人脸。这见于[[邦納症候群|邦納症候群]], {{le|睡前幻觉|Hypnagogia}}、 {{le|大脑脚性幻觉症|Peduncular hallucinosis}}、药物导致的[[幻觉|幻觉]]等。<ref>Jan Dirk Blom. ''A Dictionary of Hallucinations''. Springer, 2010, p. 187. ISBN 978-1-4419-1222-0</ref>

有研究表明，汽车专家在辨识汽车图片时、鸟类专家在辨识鸟的图片时，梭状回面孔区的活动程度很高。因此，提出了这样的问题：梭状回面孔区在辨识人脸时被激活，是因为人类进化的结果还是该受试者具有辨识人脸的专业知识？心理学家用一类物体称为{{tsl|en|Greeble (psychology)|greebles}}来检验上述两个冲突的假设。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Gauthier|first=I|coauthors=Behrmann M Tarr MJ|title=Can Face Recognition Really be Dissociated from Object Recognition?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cognitive-neuroscience_1999-07_11_4/page/349|journal=Journal of Cognitive Neuroscience|year=1999|volume=11|issue=4|pages=349–70|doi=10.1162/089892999563472|pmid=10471845}}</ref> 当受试者初次看到greebles，其梭状回面孔区的兴奋程度远低于看到人脸的时候。受试者熟悉了greebles或者说变成了greeble专家，其梭状回面孔区在看到人连与greeble的兴奋程度相当。类似地，自闭症儿童在与人脸识别相同部位产生受损的对象识别。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Scherf|first=S|coauthors=Behrmann M Minshew N Luna B|title=Atypical Development of Face and Greeble Recognition in Autism|journal=Journal of Child Psychiatry|date=April 2008|volume=49|issue=8|pages=838–47|doi=10.1111/j.1469-7610.2008.01903.x}}</ref> 后续研究表明自闭症患者的梭状回面孔区具有很低的神经元密度。<ref>{{cite journal|last=van Kooten|first=IA|coauthors=Palmen SJ, von Cappeln P, Steinbusch HW, Korr H, Heinsen H, Hof PR, van Engeland H, Schmitz C.|title=Neurons in the Fusiform Gyrus are Fewer and Smaller in Autism|journal=Brain|date=April 2008|volume=131|issue=4|pages=987–99|doi=10.1093/brain/awn033}}</ref>这产生如下问题：较少的神经元导致了不良的人脸认知，还是自闭症患者很少的人脸感知导致了神经元数量的下降？<ref>{{cite book|last=Gazzaniga|first=Michael|title=Cognitive Neuroscience: The Biology of the Mind|url=https://archive.org/details/cognitiveneurosc0000gazz|year=2014|publisher=W.W. Norton Company Inc.|location=New York City|isbn=978-00393913484|page=[https://archive.org/details/cognitiveneurosc0000gazz/page/247 247]}}</ref>更简单的问题是：人脸是每个人都具有专业识别知识的对象？ 
-
[[File:Hanyu_trad_simp.svg|thumbnail]] 有证据表明梭状回面孔区中负责人脸识别的区域的功能是进化而得。其他研究发现了人脑中专门负责识别所处环境与身体的区域。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Epstein|first=Russell|coauthors=Kanwisher, Nancy|title=A cortical representation of the local visual environment|journal=Nature|date=April 1998|volume=392|issue=6676|pages=598–601|doi=10.1038/33402|pmid=9560155}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Downing|first=Paul|coauthors=Yuhong Jiang, Miles Shuman, Nancy Kanwisher|title=A Cortical Area Selective for Visual Processing of the Human Body|journal=Science|date=September 2001|volume=293|issue=5539|pages=2470–2473|doi=10.1126/science.1063414|pmid=11577239}}</ref> 对汉字识别的研究表明，对应的梭状回面孔区中具有很高兴奋的区域与响应人脸识别的区域不同。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Fu|first=S|coauthors=Chunliang F Shichun G Yuejia L Raja P|title=Neural Adaptation Provides Evidence for Categorical Differences in Processing of Faces and Chinese Characters: an ERP Study of the N170|journal=PLoS One|year=2012|volume=7|issue=7|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0041103|editor1-last=Barton|editor1-first=Jason Jeremy Sinclair|pages=e41103|pmid=22911750|pmc=3404057}}</ref>这意味着梭状回面孔区中的特定区域进化成专责人脸识别功能。 

在具有字形→颜色[[联觉|联觉]]症的人当中，发现了梭状回的活动。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://neurophilosophy.wordpress.com/2007/05/29/imaging-of-connectivity-in-the-synaesthetic-brain/ |title=Imaging of connectivity in the synaesthetic brain « Neurophilosophy<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-17 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317111754/http://neurophilosophy.wordpress.com/2007/05/29/imaging-of-connectivity-in-the-synaesthetic-brain/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[MIT|MIT]]的一项研究表明，左、右梭状回在认知中具有不同的角色，随后二者又会互联。左梭状回负责识别类似于人脸的视觉对象的特征，而右梭状回负责确定这些被识别出来的类似人脸的视觉对象是否真是人脸。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2011/face-perception-0109.html |title=Trafton, A. "How does our brain know what is a face and what’s not?" MIT News |accessdate=2014-03-17 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317110951/http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/2011/face-perception-0109.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

